      <p>Our online classes are designed to provide students with a flexible and convenient way to learn. These classes are taught by experienced educators who use a range of engaging and interactive teaching methods to support students' learning. Our online classes are ideal for students who are unable to attend our offline classes or who prefer to learn at their own pace.</p>
      </div>
    <div id="offline-classes" class="section">
      <h3>Offline Classes</h3>
      <p>For students who prefer a traditional classroom experience, we offer offline classes at our state-of-the-art learning centers. These classes are taught by experienced educators who use a range of teaching methods to support students' learning. Our offline classes are ideal for students who thrive in a structured learning environment and who benefit from face-to-face interactions with teachers and peers.</p>
